{"id": 2624, "genre": 1001, "title": "什么细节让你觉得自己不适合一份工作？", "description": "干活没动力，同事聊不来，留在这我的人生一片灰暗。（题图来自：iStock ©️ munandme）", "record_count": 4313, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181112222651biGI9xCKaOjHZ6pD.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-11-16T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 311552, "content": "你这点钱很难让我给你办事情啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505778}, {"id": 311553, "content": "掉头发速度过快", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1426868}, {"id": 312065, "content": "限制太多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345390}, {"id": 311298, "content": "与同事三观不符，上司目光短浅。", "image": null, "praise_count": 67, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634623}, {"id": 311554, "content": "当我明知道我应该积极主动去学习去研究的内容，但没有动力去做的时候。事实上，它已经让我很失望了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505820}, {"id": 311555, "content": "与同事能否处理好关系 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379435}, {"id": 311556, "content": "有朋友说 因为\n胃不好，大饼吃不了。\n腰不好，大锅背不了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456744}, {"id": 311301, "content": "工匠精神应该是制造研发，不是年复一年日复一日做订单做文件……", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1243870}, {"id": 311557, "content": "又有朋友说，因为\n看一眼，未来就在眼前；\n再看一眼，未来又看不见啦!", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456744}, {"id": 311558, "content": "拖延癌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505842}, {"id": 311303, "content": "不合群", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208515}, {"id": 311559, "content": "投入与回报比明显低于同行和手上其他任务的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505841}, {"id": 311304, "content": "能够看到留在这里的不喜欢的未来", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1502179}, {"id": 311560, "content": "不合群\n不开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373857}, {"id": 311305, "content": "同事不注意卫生，把公司的卫生间造的脏兮兮的，很恶心，从不打扫卫生", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1504558}, {"id": 311561, "content": "男朋友都听不下去吐槽了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723325}, {"id": 311306, "content": "厕所真的蛮重要的。一个tiny bladder说道。", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498034}, {"id": 311308, "content": "说白了，歧视和偏见。你我他从不能认真公平对待彼此。优秀的公司和优秀的员工密不可分。只不过，平庸的是大多数。", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137990}, {"id": 311310, "content": "公司里得过且过，安于现在的风气，还有领导只画大饼，瞎bb", "image": null, "praise_count": 140, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1347821}, {"id": 311567, "content": "被孩子气疯了的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505907}, {"id": 311568, "content": "钱少事多运营不规范", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505905}, {"id": 311314, "content": "死气沉沉，上级压榨下级，没有前途。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 448499}, {"id": 311570, "content": "看不到尽头", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505924}, {"id": 311571, "content": "跟你谈远景，谈理想，就是不谈工资待遇", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505950}, {"id": 312083, "content": "公司管理体制", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1509683}, {"id": 311572, "content": "没激情没成就感", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 843537}, {"id": 313108, "content": "过分透支身体，没有成长空间，学不到新东西，每天做的工作在外面很难找到相应工作与相应工资，公司宫斗严重，上级过分压榨下属，对前途感到异常焦虑，不知道前方的路该如何走。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514752}, {"id": 311317, "content": "办公室抽烟的人很多，被慢性咽炎", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1504584}, {"id": 314133, "content": "负能量开始多的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678534}, {"id": 311318, "content": "三年没涨工资，没有年终奖项目奖，只有几千块死工资。公司销量一路下滑，领导层只会意淫触底反弹……根本没有底怎么反弹？", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462277}, {"id": 311574, "content": "经典的判定原则很适用：钱、工作内容、一起工作的人，三个有两个不行，就要完。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142910}, {"id": 311319, "content": "感觉不到自己在进步", "image": null, "praise_count": 68, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1503070}, {"id": 311575, "content": "钱少事少离家近", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461047}, {"id": 311320, "content": "喝酒文化", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1320768}, {"id": 311576, "content": "跟朋友见面的越来越少，用时间换钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 41676}, {"id": 311321, "content": "干不进去，那哪都别扭\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 813738}, {"id": 311577, "content": "不想熬夜coding", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1480378}, {"id": 311322, "content": "没有发展前途", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461512}, {"id": 311323, "content": "脱发", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 324758}, {"id": 311579, "content": "整个单位气氛就像一滩死水，没有正能量，大家都在混日子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506042}, {"id": 311835, "content": "不开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 832055}, {"id": 311324, "content": "总是觉得下班时间还很长", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1503244}, {"id": 311325, "content": "加不完的班...", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1449376}, {"id": 313117, "content": "钱少事多，好多事情有心无力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514915}, {"id": 311326, "content": "宫斗超过工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 255, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1168967}, {"id": 311582, "content": "还在读大学，可是不喜欢将来就业的工作也不知道该怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1486531}, {"id": 311327, "content": "自己没有提高 感觉在浪费生命…… ", "image": null, "praise_count": 369, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497840}, {"id": 311583, "content": "付出的，与收获的不成正比。（福利不好）", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505218}, {"id": 311328, "content": "企业文化 价值观", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496811}, {"id": 311584, "content": "付出的，与收获的不成正比。（福利不好）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505218}]}